episodes.title: S4 Episode 3 - #Cults
episodes.description: In this episode, Jamaine and Kathryn discuss the rise of cults in America and the polarized nature of society. They explore the attraction to cults and the tactics used to manipulate individuals. The conversation also touches on the different types of cults and the levels of control they exert over their members.
